nodes.text: The Malicious Moondog was a cantina located on the planet Suba. Sometime after the end of the Clone Wars, the Dressellian smuggler Has Obitt was on Rajtiri and made his way to the Wanton Wellspring. He thought the cantina was no more nastier than the Malicious Moondog.

The Malicious Moondog was first mentioned in the 2016 canon novel Catalyst: A Rogue One Novel, which was written by James Luceno. The novel served as a prequel to the Star Wars Anthology film, Rogue One: A Star Wars Story.
